HEADWORD: Astringer
<hw>As*trin"ger</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>ostreger</ets>, OF. <ets>ostrucier</ets>, F. <ets>autoursier</ets>,
fr. OF. <ets>austour</ets>, <ets>ostor</ets>, hawk, F.
<ets>autour</ets>; cf. L. <ets>acceptor</ets>, for <ets>accipiter</ets>,
hawk.]</ety> <def>A falconer who keeps a goshawk.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <au>Shak.</au> <au>Cowell.</au> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>austringer</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
